===Noun===
'''Polonaise'''
# The Polish language.
# An article of [[dress]] for women, consisting of a body and an outer skirt in one piece.
# {{music}} A stately Polish [[dance]] tune, in 3-4 measure, beginning always on the [[beat]] with a [[quaver]] followed by a [[crotchet]], and closing on the beat after a strong accent on the second beat; also, a dance adapted to such music; a [[polacca]].

